NEGATIVE PROMPT (do not allow)

“no extra people, no additional bags, no brand changes, no missing GUCCI text, no hat, no open hair, no smile, no heavy makeup, no harsh flash, no dramatic colored lighting, no bokeh balls, no rain, no snow, no indoor setting, no different table, no different cup color, no sneakers, no boots, no swapped outfit colors, no exaggerated shoulders, no cartoon/anime, no painterly look, no over-sharpening,', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G9y9sXHbUAAy_OW.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/SimplyAnnisa/status/2007688107337101560", "sourcePublishedAt": "2026-01-04T05:38:40.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Anissa\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/SimplyAnnisa\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
