VALUES ('Cyber-Noir City Typography Visualization Prompt', 'A complex, multi-phase prompt for generating a cinematic, high-contrast visualization of a city name (e.g., NYC Noir) using typography formed by the absence of buildings. The skyscrapers are arranged to create letter-shaped canyons, with the street level glowing with intense neon reflections bouncing off wet pavement, creating a Blade Runner meets Gotham aesthetic.', '<instructions>
