Aerial oblique shot, golden hour desert light, crisp dramatic shadows, photoreal erosion detail, minimal haze, swiss 2x2 grid composition.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G9iu5AYXYAAiHq-.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/Gdgtify/status/2007240742779998601", "sourcePublishedAt": "2026-01-03T00:01:00.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Gadgetify\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/Gdgtify\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
