ted character''s surroundings.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G9uJhbwasAc3PHn.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/harboriis/status/2007349298359607438", "sourcePublishedAt": "2026-01-03T07:12:22.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Harboriis\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/harboriis\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
