INSERT INTO cinematic_prompts (title, description, prompt_text, category, tags, image_urls, metadata)
VALUES ('64K Cinematic Punk Portrait Image Transformation', 'A highly detailed prompt for an image-to-image transformation, instructing the model to convert an uploaded image into a 64K resolution, ultra-detailed cinematic portrait of a rebellious, punk-inspired woman. The prompt locks the face identity and specifies complex details like mismatched eye makeup, pastel-dyed pigtails, distressed clothing, tattoos, and a gritty urban background with a ''WANTED'' poster.', 'Transform this image [Upload Your Image] into a 64K DSLR shot resolution of cinematic, ultra-detailed portrait of a rebellious, punk-inspired woman (same face as the uploaded image) standing confidently against a rough, cracked concrete wall. A weathered “WANTED” poster is partially visible behind her head, adding a gritty, outlaw atmosphere. She is leaning back casually with her arms crossed, projecting a mischievous, dangerous confidence. She has very pale, porcelain skin and striking light-colored eyes, enhanced with bold, smudged eye makeup-one eye accented with dark eyeliner and the other with a bluish shadow. A small heart-shaped face marking sits just beneath one eye. Her lips are painted a deep red, forming a playful yet sinister smirk. Her platinum-blonde hair is styled into high twin pigtails, with the ends dyed in contrasting pastel tones-one side faded pink and the other teal blue. Loose strands frame her face, adding a messy, chaotic charm. She wears a distressed, torn, fitted white T-shirt with faded red sleeves and a grungy printed slogan across the chest. The shirt appears worn and dirty, with frayed edges and holes, emphasizing a raw, post-apocalyptic or urban-crime aesthetic. Leather straps and suspenders rest over her shoulders. Her arms are decorated with tattoos in bold, sketchy lettering and symbols, and she wears chunky metal bracelets and cuffs on her wrists. A thick metallic choker encircles her neck. Around her waist is a

studded belt, contributing to the punk-rock vibe. The lighting is moody and directional, highlighting facial contours and textures while casting soft shadows for depth. The color palette is muted and gritty, with desaturated grays and earthy tones contrasted by the vibrant pastel hair colors and red accents. The overall style is hyper-realistic, cinematic, edgy, and dark, with a high level of texture detail-skin pores, fabric wear, cracks, and paper creases all clearly visible.

