VALUES ('Film Noir Cinematic Portrait Prompt', 'A detailed prompt for generating a high-contrast cinematic black-and-white studio portrait of a man, using a reference image for identity. It specifies dramatic low-key lighting with strong rim highlights, deep shadows, film-noir aesthetic, and technical details like a 3:4 aspect ratio and subtle film grain.', 'A high-contrast cinematic black-and-white studio portrait of a man in the uploaded image with an athletic build. Three-quarter body portrait, vertical 3:4 aspect ratio. He stands left-of-center, torso slightly angled, head turned to the left, gazing off-camera with a serious, contemplative expression. Full, well-groomed beard, textured hair, intense focused eyes with glasses. He’s wearing a slim-fit dark long-sleeve henley shirt in a charcoal-to-black tone. Accessories include a wristwatch on his left wrist, a bracelet on his right wrist, and a ring on his right hand. Shot from a slightly low angle. Dramatic low-key cinematic lighting with a strong rear-right side light creating bold rim highlights along the jawline, shoulders, and arms. Minimal to no fill light, deep shadows, high contrast. A visible studio light appears in the background, with light haze or smoke adding atmospheric diffusion. Studio environment with a soft, smoky, obscured background and significant dark negative space on the right side of the frame. Subject in sharp focus with shallow to moderate depth of field, background softly diffused. Subtle film grain, wide dynamic range, rich blacks, detailed mid-gray skin tones, bright edge highlights. Moody, intense, film-noir-inspired editorial portrait suggesting strength, introspection, and quiet tension.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G9erHQUaoAAg_mu.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/rovvmut_/status/2006260304834093286", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-31T07:05:05.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Heisenberg\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/rovv