VALUES ('Four Seasons Puzzle for 2026 New Year Greeting', 'A highly detailed, multi-panel prompt for Nano Banana Pro, inspired by a previous puzzle prompt. It generates a 2x2 grid photo showing the same female character in outfits representing Winter, Spring, Summer, and Autumn, each holding a piece of a glowing magic puzzle that converges in the center to spell ''2026 New Year''s Day Happy''. The prompt emphasizes visual consistency and a cinematic, high-definition aesthetic.', '一张 2x2 的四宫格构图摄影，展示同一位女性主角在四个不同的季节奇幻场景中，亲手拼凑出新年魔法拼图。
[左上格，冬季蓝主题]：同一位女性，冰雪王后装扮，穿着缀满冰晶的海军蓝礼服。她双手托举着一块巨大的蓝色发光冰晶拼图块，上面刻有数字“20”，正向画面中心移动。眼神专注，背景是极光下的冰川与漫天飞雪。
[右上格，春季粉主题]：同一位女性，花之精灵装扮，穿着樱花粉色蕾丝裙。她双手托举着一块缠绕着盛开花朵的粉色发光拼图块，上面刻有数字“26”，眼神充满期待。背景是梦幻的樱花林和飞舞的蝴蝶。
[左下格，夏季绿主题]：同一位女性，森林女神装扮，穿着薄荷绿色的自然风格连衣裙。她双手向上托举着一块蕴含森林能量的绿色翡翠拼图块，上面刻有“元旦”字样，表情认真。背景是阳光穿透的繁茂森林和发光的萤火虫。
[右下格，秋季黄主题]：同一位女性，流金岁月装扮，穿着柠檬黄色向日葵礼服。她推入最后一块金黄色琥珀材质的拼图块，上面刻有“快乐”字样。她头向后仰，爆发出成功的喜悦笑容。背景是金色的落日麦田。
[中心视觉锁定]：四块拼图在画面中心完美咬合，迸发出包含冰晶、花瓣、绿叶和金光的夺目光芒，在中心汇聚成清晰的汉字“2026元旦快乐”。
[统一渲染]：电影级唯美光效，超高清画质，极高细节处理，保持人物面部特征在四格中完全一致。', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G9ayv2kWIAE_1vt.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/Adam38363368936/status/2005987897598791730", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-30T13:02:38.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Adam\u4e5f\u53eb\u5409\u7c73\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/Adam38363368936\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
ON CONFLICT (title) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO cinematic_prompts (title, description, prompt_text, category, tags, image_urls, metadata)
VALUES ('Reality Glitch Documentary Image Prompt: Low-Poly Deer in Headlights', 'An image generation prompt designed to create a surreal, glitch-art documentary scene. It features a low-poly, flat-shaded gray deer (a geometric mesh) that has failed to load its textures, caught in the blinding headlights of a vehicle. The scene is set in a hyper-realistic forest at night, emphasizing the contrast between the sterile mathematical perfection of the glitch and the gritty natural environment, captured with a trail cam aesthetic and digital imperfections.', '{
