VALUES ('Identity-Preserving Storybook Illustration', 'A structured prompt to transform a subject from an uploaded image into a warm, cheerful storybook illustration using colored pencils and soft watercolor washes, strictly preserving the subject''s identity, facial structure, and likeness while adopting a cute, semi-cartoon style.', '{
