VALUES ('Historical Archivist Prompt for Flawed Inventions', 'A complex, multi-phase prompt designed for the AI to act as a Historical Archivist, generating a photorealistic macro photograph of a container overflowing with the physical forms of four obscure, failed historical prototypes from a user-specified era, complete with legible, handwritten labels detailing the invention and its fatal flaw.', 'Role: Historical Archivist & Technical Illustrator.
