}', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G9ZN99rboAAR3Qi.jpg","https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G9ZN-AlbYAAHoFY.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/GaganSingh8u/status/2005876446821335249", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-30T05:39:46.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Gagan Singh\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/GaganSingh8u\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
