},
"negative_prompt": "杂乱，暖色调（除了温和的点缀），复古风，手写体，低分辨率，模糊，文字扭曲，甚至噪点，深色背景，不卫生，过饱和，水印，食物质感，过于冷冰冰的临床感，恐慌性的警示图标"
}', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G9WQV2GbwAAeih1.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/0xwolverines/status/2005670265032941657", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-29T16:00:29.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"0xwolverine\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/0xwolverines\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
