VALUES ('Candid Luxury Bathroom Portrait (Identity Locked)', 'An extensive prompt focused on generating a hyper-realistic, candid medium shot of a young woman sitting on a marble bathroom vanity. It uses strict identity locking, specifies a {argument name="dress type" default="short satin slip dress"}, and details the environment, lighting (cinematic side lighting with striped shadows), and camera style (35mm film aesthetic).', 'Using my photo as a strict and non-negotiable reference, preserve 100% of my facial identity — exact facial features, proportions, bone structure, skin texture, and natural expression.
